A minimalistic illustration of a sleek web form floating in empty white space, with several input fields rendered as clean rectangular boxes. Most fields are calm gray, but one field near the top glows with a soft red pulsing border, with a subtle spotlight effect drawing the eye directly to it. A single elegant cursor arrow gracefully points toward the highlighted field, suggesting automatic navigation. The composition uses generous negative space, muted colors with the red accent creating visual hierarchy, and clean geometric shapes conveying precision and user-focused design.
